    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Understood, I note you even say this in the note itself.</p>",
        "id": 260296832,
        "sender_full_name": "Oliver Nash",
        "timestamp": 1636043425
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Yeah, that lemma should be formulated something like <code>times_cont_diff f -&gt; times_cont_diff g -&gt; times_cont_diff Œª x, (f x) (g x)</code> where <code>f : X -&gt; (E ‚ÜíL[ùïú] F)</code> and <code>g : X -&gt; E</code></p>",
